data.description: Come see this beautiful home located minutes from shopping, entertainment, and medical services. Kitchen and bathrooms were renovated in 2019. Updates since 2019:new roof 2023, added covered patio, new clean outs, foundation stabilized 2022, drip system, improved backyard privacy fence, upgraded electrical panel and added solar. Exterior was painted in 2015. Kitchen appliances new in 2019 except the refrigerator. Tons of natural light! Fenced backyard with a shed for storage. Mature fruit trees with views of Mingus Mountain! No HOA!
